{"tid":2264384,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸記錄+你問我答","createTime":"2020-10-30T15:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T13:21:59.000Z","uid":367078,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"30f7d31c9c1439a5c561dfe82fd54de82f01829a","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"交代下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身係不停爆石頭瘡，嚟M之前+期間會爆得仲多，本身好咗嘅地方隔一排又爆過<br />\n有埋毛孔粗大同埋紅印問題，啲紅印要差唔多半年先退到<br />\n生咗7年暗瘡實在忍無可忍<br />\n上星期終於的起心肝睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過藥費成800一個禮拜真係好貴<br />\n諗緊好唔好轉睇其他醫生<br />\n暫時嚟講皮膚出少咗油同冇乜再爆石頭瘡，不過仲有啲細細粒嘅暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a2916e6e6ceb80a0d71f0dd520bed2ff292b29","tid":2264384,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"相呢"},{"pid":"1f11ee36f661e88a44df6eda56c8e85086e7f38f","tid":2264384,"uid":18222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"睇個邊個醫生？ 我都想睇"},{"pid":"ae85582861e2ea198cd74c96d6766f478540b1e6","tid":2264384,"uid":363071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"幾耐先見到個效果?"},{"pid":"8cbd52344c9cccb5ffe0e099a37f82221706f3b0","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"講漏咗而家係食緊40mg一日 早晚各20mg咁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y2LdAL6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2LdAL6.jpg&h=64de01dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92d306fc466e387a5f33be4803d3a7bfae709dea","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae85582861e2ea198cd74c96d6766f478540b1e6","tid":2264384,"uid":363071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"幾耐先見到個效果?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"醫生話要食住半年先，半年之後視乎情況再