 />\n做運動（冇乜分別都係繼續爆瘡不過個人會開朗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n用酸（有用）我係晚晚都會搽，少好多粉刺，無咁易爆瘡）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"用酸係咩黎架 <br />\n感謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"用緊detclear個啫喱同埋the ordinary lactic acid 10% <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrxoJWm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrxoJWm.jpg&h=29b7cb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCWkL9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCWkL9H.jpg&h=78ec10f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前亦都有用過rosette紅色嗰支去角質啫喱同埋dr wu杏仁酸，但可能我皮膚出油太犀利所以效果唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21d111fd0905ec295472261eab896fe54a777fd","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"至於茶樹油，好多牌子都試過晒但無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暗瘡貼嚟講覺得萬秀雷敦嗰個吸油吸得最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過手頭緊嘅話用3M嗰款都OK<br />\n暗瘡膏就推薦白兔牌 搽上去之後會變乾唔會痴笠笠 同埋會變啡啡地色可以令啲紅印睇落淡啲 oxy5 oxy 10消暗瘡都ok 不過嫌佢會嗱傷口同埋無咁快變乾，搞到頭髮痴住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c49d58825325d02654232e6623cb0c88ca6372","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a21d111fd0905ec295472261eab896fe54a777fd","tid":2264384,"uid":367078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"至於茶樹油，好多牌子都試過晒但無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暗瘡貼嚟講覺得萬秀雷敦嗰個吸油吸得最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過手頭緊嘅話用3M嗰款都OK<br />\n暗瘡膏就推薦白兔牌 搽上去之後會變乾唔會痴笠笠 同埋會變啡啡地色可以令啲紅印睇落淡啲 oxy5 oxy 10消暗瘡都ok 不過嫌佢會嗱傷口同埋無咁快變乾，搞到頭髮痴住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c